## 🏗️ Boilerplate Module Features

The `hackathon_module` template includes:

### Models (3 models)
- **HackathonRecord** — Main model with state workflow, chatter, computed fields, smart buttons
- **HackathonRecordLine** — Line model with quantity × price = subtotal
- **HackathonTag** — Tag model with color support

### Views (7 view types)
- **Form** — Header with status buttons + statusbar, smart buttons, tabs, chatter
- **List** — Color-coded rows, badges, avatars, sum columns
- **Kanban** — Grouped by state, progress bar, priority stars, user avatars
- **Search** — Quick filters, group-by options, date filters
- **Graph** — Bar chart by state
- **Pivot** — Cross-tab analysis
- **Calendar** — Date-based view

### Other
- **Security** — User/Manager groups + model access CSV
- **Demo data** — 3 sample records, 4 tags, 2 line items
- **API Controller** — 3 REST endpoints (list, create, stats)
- **Wizard** — Bulk state change with optional note

