## 🚀 How to Use on Hackathon Day

### Step 1: Read the problem statement
Open [04_PROBLEM_SOLVING_PLAYBOOK.md](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/odoo/docs/04_PROBLEM_SOLVING_PLAYBOOK.md) and classify the problem.

### Step 2: Copy the boilerplate
```powershell
Copy-Item -Recurse custom_addons\hackathon_module custom_addons\your_solution_name
```

### Step 3: Rename everything
- Folder name → `your_solution_name`
- `_name` in models → `your.domain.model`
- All XML IDs → update prefixes
- `__manifest__.py` → update name, description, depends

### Step 4: Start Odoo
```powershell
.\venv\Scripts\python.exe odoo-src\odoo-bin -c odoo.conf -d hackathon -i your_solution_name --dev=all
```

### Step 5: Build!
Follow the timeline in [00_HACKATHON_BATTLECARD.md](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/odoo/docs/00_HACKATHON_BATTLECARD.md).

